{"tid":842721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持槍匪劫尖沙嘴The ONE錶行60萬名錶","createTime":"2018-09-30T14:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:24:11.000Z","uid":104138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd632e47aa51f97ec9b82a346391bf39c484c59","tid":842721,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"消息稱，匪徒身穿深色西裝入內扮作顧客，從衫袋內取出一把手槍指嚇男職員，3秒內擸走放在枱面的3隻名錶<br />\n尖沙嘴晚上發生行劫案！晚上近8時，尖沙嘴The ONE地下的OMEGA專門店遭賊人劫走3隻名錶，共值約60萬元，職員其後報警求助，大批警員穿著避彈衣，荷槍實彈到場調查，在附近兜截並無發現，正翻查舖頭的閉路電視，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n據悉，匪徒大約晚上7時半左右入店內，當時他身穿深色西裝在店內兜遊，至20分鐘後才向職員訛稱要求購買多隻名錶。職員當時不虞有詐，在飾櫃內取出名錶，匪徒突然從衫袋內取出一把手槍指嚇男職員，3秒內擸走放在枱面的3隻名錶，之後跑離錶行往重慶大廈方向逃走。"},{"pid":"53310ba8eb7391dcef3896ebf7ec5625a0bd43d1","tid":842721,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180930/58742411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58742411&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8je8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=14dd2bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58742411&h=8e8ce035\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180930/58742411</a>"},{"pid":"501ffaa249d7207d0eaf8959234b377b285f7473","tid":842721,"uid":38666,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"又拉唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fed1ba520dabdfe58a5681f34b0a381d5beedc0","tid":842721,"uid":149566,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cls愈嚟愈多人打劫"},{"pid":"6eaed06d340a4d846fb10ec44d